        "Note 3: Must use OnQ system. HPMS software proprietary to HSS. Refresh every 3 years.",
        "Note 4: Restaurant Brands optional. Initial fee nonrefundable.",
        "Note 5: HSM procurement agency; fee is 4-10% of project cost plus product cost, freight, tax."
